Dear Winner
We congratulate you over your success in the following official
publication of results of the E-mail electronic online Sweepstakes
organized by Microsoft  Lottery Promotion, in conjunction with  Free
Lotto Company  Inc  for the promotion of software products, (F.P.S.)
held on the 24th of September ,2021  in London, United Kingdom.

We write to officially notify you of this award  that  was released
with the following particulars attached to it.

(1) Award numbers: MLAT#2010
(2) Email ticket numbers: 1587-5896-4598-87
(3) Batch numbers: 850THL#2010
(4) The file reference numbers: MLY-Y/250-450890
(5) Serial Numbers: McST/776/ML10101
(6)  Amount. US$750,000.00

For further details , Email us your Full Names, Address, Telephone
Number & Occupation

Mr Steve Edward
Validating Officer
(Product Marketing)
